{
  "stem": "3097.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they thought about fighting or going to Romania, smuggle themselves, you see, that way, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They tried to do something, but the hostile population-- the hostile population in Poland prevented many, many people who maybe could accomplish a lot, from surviving, or doing even that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "August 1942, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "August 1492-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --at about 3 o'clock or 4 o'clock, they started to knock-- the Jewish police started to knock on our door.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew something will happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "August 20th-- August 20.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew that something will happen, because there used to be an outfit by the name of Sliwa, S-L-I-W-A-- where they use a woodworking outfit.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they used to make small ramps for the railroad-- steps-- to get in, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was some rumors that they will take the people and send them east.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They will evacuate us to work someplace there, by train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we thought that they will go there and to-- we work some-- east.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we were waiting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So when the time-- they surrounded the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Polish police, Ukrainians, SS, Gestapo, they surrounded the area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a special place-- oh, they knocked on the door.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And even I understood Russian, but the Ukrainians talk Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], you know-- get up, and get out, you see?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they started to beat the people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People started to take with them a lot of stuff.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had to lose it, because they-- you know, you couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- they beat you, and they throw you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father had to prepare before, a special place there on [NON-ENGLISH] Street, which was like a quadrangle-- a big quadrangle, where they did accumulate all those concentrated-- all those people.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They split the city in three areas for the evacuation.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
